title: Star Traders: Frontiers v2.0.41
description: Command your ship and crew as a space pirate, merchant, bounty hunter, and more in Star Traders: Frontiers  an epic space RPG from Trese Brothers Games. Venture forth into a massive open universe, rich with adventure and the lore of the Star Traders. Choose your path by assembling and commanding your custom crew and spaceship in a constantly evolving galaxy torn by internal strife, political intrigue, and alien threats.
